fields.title: Alderaan
fields.content:
## Milestones

* Onboarded our first two clients to the platform
* Updated the web application to the new branding
* Completed Total Addressable Market Analysis & Modeling web views

## Features

* UI Component: Market Size Map (ticket #164087086)
* UI View: Total Addressable Market (ticket #164223104)
* UI View Mod: Acquisition Funnel Re-Design (ticket #164176117)
* UI View: Modeling (ticket #164088038)
* Django Route: Load static TAM data from local file system (ticket #164127938)
* Django Route: Loading static modeling data from local file system (ticket #164127939)
* UI Component: Button Group (ticket #164182899)
* Add meaningful <title> for each page (ticket #164488236)
* UI Component: Modeling Comparison (ticket #164088130)
* UI View: Add '4-Week Average' to Acquisition Funnel, Volume of Activity (ticket #164502616)
* Rebrand Work (ticket #164549346)
* Cut DNS over to Route53 (ticket #164648812)

## Bugs

* UI View Mod: Rent to Income Ratio (ticket #164479371)
* El Cortez - Change Leasable/Occupiable Units KPI to pull most recent entry (ticket #164478795)
* El Cortez - Override Leased Units to = 113 (ticket #164478763)
* UI View Mod: Limit Map Movement (Click and Drag) Function (ticket #164479394)
* Acquisition funnel "Volume of app" primary data value and delta are mis-formatted (ticket #164559037)
* Acquisition and retention investment amounts have improperly formatted deltas (ticket #164559010)
* Campaign Investment box layout and numerical formatting is buggy (ticket #164558982)
* Campaign URL leads to a Django Error page (ticket #164590391)
* UI View Mod: Estimated Revenue Change '+' or '-' in Remarkably blue (ticket #164478961)
* UI View Mod: ROMI 'X' in Remarkably blue (ticket #164478824)
* UI View Mod: Remove '0' from Volume of Activity in Acquisition Funnel (ticket #164479154)
* LeasingPerformanceReport: Cannot read property 'end' of undefined (ticket #164503330)
* Retention Delta appears incorrect (ticket #164590434)
* 4-Week Average Figure Not Populating from Data (ticket #164586537)
* Colored negative values don't always display correctly (ticket #164556186)
* USV > EXE Formatting (ticket #164558261)
* Income to Rent Chart rounds Rents incorrectly (ticket #164613869)

fields.title: Bespin
fields.content:
## Milestones

* Delivered software to first two clients
* Built release tracking system
* Extended Rebranding to Login/Password Recovery page
* Added Funnel Performance Analysis
* Built a demo dataset for sales and event usage
* Fixed a slew of styling bugs in advance of the CRE Tech event in Los Angeles

## Features

* Rebrand client login (ticket #164560780)
* Make Client Login the Homepage (ticket #164648878)
* Rebrand client password recovery (ticket #164560822)
* TAM Map: Change Map Colors (ticket #164813311)
* Release Notes Index/Details Page (ticket #164674884)
* Add Jest and Enzyme to the project for testing (ticket #164648581)
* UI View Mod: Update Baseline Report to include new Funnel Performance Analysis Component (ticket #164183059)
* UI Component: Funnel Performance Analysis (Weekly) (ticket #164182981)
* UI Component: Funnel Performance Analysis (Monthly) (ticket #164183032)
* Backend Mod: Add properties for Funnel Performance Analysis Component (ticket #164781969)
* Mod Component: CampaignInvestmentReport - Color Change, Y-Axis Change (ticket #164813683)

## Bugs

* Bug: Adjust End Date on Date Range to be inclusive End (ticket #164711563)
* Bug: Target USV > EXE percentage missing decimal point (ticket #164711478)
* Bug: Cost Pers are Noted as Percentages (ticket #164711442)
* Modeling: Styling Issues (ticket #164818137)

fields.title: Coruscant
fields.content:
# Milestones

* Completed Campaign Plan View
* Completed majority of excel workflow to support Professional Services
* Integrated with Google Analytics to pull Demographic, Geographic, and Traffic Source data
* Added CircleCI for Continuous Integration to help reduce bug rates
* Added Jest & Enzyme tests to improve UI testing

# Features

* 164789805	UI View Mod: Total Market Size Donut Chart 
* 164789818	Component Mod: EstimatedMarketSizeOverview
* 164936101	Add building image to report page Chrome
* 164649128	Django Admin Mod: Add Thumbnail and Fullsize Photo to Project Class
* 164998422	Mod Campaign Plan endpoint to pass the CP Props JSON
* 164675540	Add Custom Property to Google Analytics for Property ID
* 165099960	Add precise_start and precise_end parameters to all multiperiod and date sequence APIs
* 165073633	Add average tenant age to Project model
* 165073608	Move highest, average, and lowest monthly rent to Project model
* 165073673	Remove leases_due_to_expire and target_leases_due_to_expire from Period
* 165073813	Support arbitrary model spreadsheet types
* 164976129	Connect CircleCI to Github
* 164976127	Setup Continuous Integration: Circle CI
* 165187395	Add total_units to Project model.
* 165043781	Total Market Analysis Import UI
* 165073713	Remove targets from baseline+perf spreadsheet
* 165073701	Remove average and lowest monthly rent from baseline+perf spreadsheet template
* 165068068	Python Library: Request Unique Site Visitors for a Website Broken Down by Age
* 165200445	Bug: Take Most Recent Target Leased Rate for All Reports
* 165073872	Finalize baseline+perf importer (CLI and UI)
* 165073910	Finalize Campaign Plan Importer (CLI and UI)
* 165033300	Add a basic shallow render unit test to all UIComponents
* 165032515	UI Component: Overview Tab in Campaign Plan
* 165032583	UIComponent: Demand Creation Tab in Campaign Plan
* 165136110	Update Favicon Image to New Branding
* 165032682	UIComponent: Generic Tab for Campaign Plan
* 164649078	UI View Mod: Add 'Total Number of Units' to Leased Rate and Occupied Rate
* 164992424	Finalize Campaign Plan Importer (CLI and UI)
* 164478728	Modeling Excel Template 
* 165032753	View Mod: Modify the Campaign Plan View to use new React Components
* 165157317	Add ability to 'Hide' or 'Show' report on live platform

# Bugs

* 164817902	Baseline Report: Styling Issues
* 164817987	Performance Report: Styling issues
* 164818098	TAM: Styling Issues
* 164907767	Funnel Performance Analysis: Do not highlight zeros
* 164912219	Bug: Fix Conversion Rates on Funnel Performance Analysis  (Monthly) 
* 164883869	Bug: Neutral Arrow Indicator Parameters
* 165063500	Bug: Heat Map Date Ranges Inaccurate
* 164884052	UI Bug: Round Investment Allocations to 1 Decimal Place
* 165130223	UI Bug: Change 'Months' to 'Weeks' in Baseline Date Range
